      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "一个分类器可能不够可靠。",
        "那如果问一群分类器呢？"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "ensemble_methods"
      ],
      "id": "s064",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "ensemble_methods"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "这就是 <term id=\"ensemble_methods\">集成方法</term> 的思想。",
        "训练多个分类器，然后让它们一起投票。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "bagging"
      ],
      "id": "s065",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "bagging",
        "bootstrap_sampling"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "第一个经典方法是 <term id=\"bagging\">Bagging</term>。",
        "它用 <term id=\"bootstrap_sampling\">自助采样</term> 生成多个不同的训练集。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s066",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "自助采样就是有放回地抽样。",
        "每个新训练集都和原始数据集一样大，但内容不同。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s067",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "在每个采样集上训练一个分类器。",
        "最终，所有分类器投票决定新样本的类别。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "boosting"
      ],
      "id": "s068",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "boosting"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "第二个方法是 <term id=\"boosting\">Boosting</term>。",
        "它和 Bagging 不同，是迭代进行的。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s069",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "每一轮，它会更关注上一轮被分错的样本。",
        "给这些样本更高的权重，让下一个分类器重点学习它们。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "random_forest"
      ],
      "id": "s070",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "random_forest"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "第三个是 <term id=\"random_forest\">随机森林</term>。",
        "它结合了 Bagging 和随机特征选择。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s071",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "每棵树都用自助采样训练。",
        "但在每个节点分裂时，只随机选择一部分特征来考虑。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s072",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "这增加了树的多样性，让整体模型更强大。",
        "随机森林是实践中非常有效的算法。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
